## Local overlay and deliberate divergences

This repo adds local files under `references/local/` and scripts under `scripts/`
to improve authoring quality on top of the upstream reference set.

Deliberate differences from upstream `skill-cli`:

- Keep `.drawio` as the visible source of truth after export
- Add layout and quality gate documents derived from real diagram failures
- Add deterministic XML and layout validators
- Support multiple agent harnesses with dedicated install docs
